resources.string: it might not mean anything to you but waking up with thoughts of how I would make you breakfast in bed after a long day at work rub your feet after fixing ur dinner and your warm bathwater. I feel like a king each time I walk by lifting my head to the heavens and whispering under my breath so my father in heaven could hear me say Thank you for the lady you gave to me. You make me want to be a better person. I bless the day I shyly approached you.

Love they say is in the eyes of the beholder and this for sure is true. you made me see life in a new light. you made me work on my insecurities and open up to not just love you but myself. loving is so easy and I wouldn\'t want to change that. thank you for loving me the way you do and opening my life and heart to love.
